description:
Systane COMPLETE is the all-in-one drop to relieve all types of dry eyes^

Are you putting up with irritated, tired, sore, watery, dry eyes?

You may be suffering from dry eyes! Systane range of lubricating eyedrops are designed to moisturise and relieve the symptoms of dry eyes.

Systane COMPLETE is the all-in-one eye drop that replenishes all layersof the tear film. Systane COMPLETE relieves irritated, tired, sore, watery,dry eyes for up to 8 hours^. Systane COMPLETE uses unique technology
to moisturise, restore and stabilise the tear film:

HP-Guar to allow retention of moisture and relieve dry eye symptoms
Nano-sized lipid droplet technology to minimise blurring and provide surface coverage on your eyes
*IQVIA 01 TEARS S1K SELL-IN VALUE MAT 2021-02. ^Dry eye and associated symptoms due to aqueous deficient, evaporative and mixed dry eye.

References: 1. Alcon Data on File, Study CDMGD0012401 (available on request). 2. TFOS DEWS II 2017. 3. Rangarajan et al. J Ocul Pharmacol Th.2019; 35(1): 32-37 (Sponsored by Novartis) 4. Springs, C. Dev Ophthalmol. 2010;45:139-147

Simple choice to relieve all types of dry eyes^

Replenishes all layers of tear film

Lasts up to 8 hours
name: Systane Complete Lubricant Eye Drop 10mL
